  <brief_title>Repeat Ablation Procedure in Patients With Relapse of Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Repeat Ablation Procedure in Patients With Relapse of Paroxysmal Atrial Fibrillation Using Reisolation of Pulmonary Vein Versus Reisolation of Pulmonary Vein With Additional Anterior Line</official_title>
